name: MT-15
description:
The MT-15 is a Pure-bred hyper naked, one of the most dynamic light weights from the MT stable. This bike has all the traits of a hyper naked with its agile handling, wide handle bar and ultra-light weight of 138 kgs.
The impeccably styled MT-15 with its Bi functional LED headlight gives the motorcycle an aggressive and intimidating look. This hyper naked bike will not only give you the thrill you seek but will also inspire immense confidence in the rider.
